Class ServiceCatalog

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ServiceCatalog
extends BaseCatalog

This class provides a holder for all information for a map service. Please note that two properties, _outputUrl and _serviceURL are not used in the current JSP sample viewers.

See Also:
